<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克告诉了伊丽莎关于奶牛米可的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爸爸是一名探险家，” 杰克又说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一天他发现了很多金子和宝物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊丽莎的眼睛亮了：“宝物？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克点了点头，说了更多关于金子和宝物的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是一个邪恶的食人魔偷走了我们的一切，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后爸爸就去世了。” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们很穷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们家也很穷。” 伊丽莎说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我父母几年前去世了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我要一个人照顾弟弟妹妹们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唉……” 杰克说，“你真的太辛苦了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊丽莎点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虽然没有钱，但是你还有妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈就是你的宝物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对，妈妈就是我的宝物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们挥手再见，杰克继续往家走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到杰克，妈妈兴奋地跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“找到工作了吗？” 妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“镇上没有人需要帮手。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈皱了皱眉头：“那我们只能卖掉米可了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克大吃一惊：“哦……不，妈妈！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们不能卖掉米可！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们需要它的牛奶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“米可已经没有牛奶了！” 妈妈坚定地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我们必须卖掉它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克又说了些什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是妈妈抱起了双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你明天必须卖掉米可！” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要钱买食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道妈妈是对的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>